    Table of links at the top:
      Data access - link to real-time and post-flight data
      Current mission status - hand-edited file updated when needed
         includes a hand-edited archive of previous status messages

    Project Description     -  brief wrietup
    Participants            -  Table with Investigator names and affiliations,
                                instrument(s) and plans for study
    IDEAS2 Email List Information  -  Link to moderated email list
    Aircraft Configuration  -  Table (clickable diagrams)
    Current Weather         -  Table with clickable dynamic information
