      Soundings    \  courtesy of
      Satellite    /  Dave Rogers
      Web Cams    /
    Weather Forecasts
      Courtesy of CSU, NCAR, RAP, NOAA, NWS courtesy of Dave Rogers
    Photo Gallery
      Unedited photos from RAF's digital camera
      Ported into a gallery courtesy of Dave Rogers
    Flight Summaries
      info posted after each test/research flight
      GOES images retrieved about an hour after end of flight
      Scientist reports sent to me and posted manually

